{"data":[{"date":"07:21 01/07","title":"Uruguay 2-1 B\u0110N: Ng\u00e0y Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi \u201csong s\u00e1t\u201d Suarez \u2013 Cavani","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/uruguay-21-bdn-ngay-ronaldo-phai-ghen-ti-voi-song-sat-suarez-cavani.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n Ronaldo im ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a World Cup. D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha g\u1ecdi t\u00ean \u201csong s\u00e1t\u201d l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </strong>Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- Uruguay:</strong> Cavani (7&rsquo;, 62&rsquo;)<br>\r\n<strong>- B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: </strong>Pepe (55&rsquo;)\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/274618/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t c\u00f3 7 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 Uruguay v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c, ch\u00ednh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ebfch v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c tr\u00e1i theo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay, Suarez treo b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 Cavani \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t cong v\u00fat c\u1ee7a Suarez cho t\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh song kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Cavani. T\u1eeb El Pistolero (Tay s\u00fang) cho t\u1edbi El Matador (D\u0169ng s\u0129 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2) \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Ronaldo ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi Suarez &ndash; Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Ronaldo ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi Suarez &ndash; Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Du-am-Uruguay-2-1-Bo-Dao-Nha-Ronaldo-ghen-ti-voi-Suarez-&ndash;-Cavani-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suarez ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Cavani m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u00ednh Cavani ph\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1nh cho Suarez. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf, ngo\u1eb7t v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Ricardo Pereira r\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00f2ng cung qua \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 Jose Fonte v\u00e0 Raphael Guerreiro. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, Cavani sau khi di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4n ngoan ph\u00e1 b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0\u1ee1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Suarez, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o trong t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 Uruguay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani va Suarez cua Uruguay\" title=\"Cavani va Suarez cua Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Cavani-va-Suarez-cua-Uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu song s\u00e1t Cavani v\u00e0 Suarez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra trong 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Cavani \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i \u0110T Uruguay, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 12 l\u00e0 do Suarez ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o (chi\u1ebfm 27%). D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tinh t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Rui Patricio, Suarez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ch\u00ecm xuy\u00ean h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i 10 ph\u00fat sau khi hi\u1ec7p 2 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc b\u1ecf l\u1ecfng Pepe \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Uruguay b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. Trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ai k\u00e8m, trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Muslera. Qua \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch 325 ph\u00fat kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ni\u1ec1m vui c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2u. Ph\u00fat 62, t\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 7 ph\u00fat sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Uruguay l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Bentancur m\u1edbm b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Cavani tung c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9n v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Patricio c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tung ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1. 2-1 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Uruguay l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190048.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190048.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span><br>\r\n<span>Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo l\u1ea1i im ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Oscar Tabarez ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 76 ph\u00fat d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Tr\u1eeb &ldquo;song s\u00e1t&rdquo; Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Uruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 2 l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 67%, hi\u1ebfm khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Uruguay ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ngo\u00e0i Pepe, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ai b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo don doc tai BDN\" title=\"Ronaldo don doc tai BDN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Ronaldo-don-doc-tai-BDN.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khai th\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martin Caceres (31 tu\u1ed5i) v\u00e0 Jose Gimenez (m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng). Nh\u01b0ng ho\u1eb7c Caceres c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Nahitan Nandez, ho\u1eb7c Gimenez v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean phong \u0111\u1ed9, CR7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ea1t ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Uruguay, Diego Godin cho Diego Laxalt, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5t d\u1ee5ng v\u00f5. Su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o l\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng k\u1ec3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i khi tranh c\u00e3i gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Suarez\" title=\"Ronaldo va Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Ronaldo-va-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 Cavani c\u00f3 Suarez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo &ldquo;t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i&rdquo; t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ee9 4, y nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Lionel Messi. Nh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean kia, h\u1eb3n CR7 h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Suarez &ndash; Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n 2 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 tr\u00ean \u0110TQG, Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nhau. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u0103n \u00fd. V\u1edbi Ronaldo, \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd anh v\u1eabn \u1edf trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Khi si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y im ti\u1ebfng, l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Seleccao g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay vuot qua BDN vao tu ket\" title=\"Uruguay vuot qua BDN vao tu ket\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Uruguay-vuot-qua-BDN-vao-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd c\u00f3 Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 c\u1ee7a Uruguay v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5t s\u1ed1ng \u1edf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 2 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Goncalo Guedes qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Sau khi Andre Silva v\u00e0o thay \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Uruguay v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. Nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. Ronaldo v\u1eabn &ldquo;t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i&rdquo; \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup trong khi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n b\u1edfi v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u:<br>\r\nUruguay (4-3-3): </strong>Muslera; Caceres, Gimenez, Godin, Laxalt; Nandez (Sanchez 81&rsquo;), Torreira, Vecino; Bentancur (Rodriguez 63&rsquo;), Suarez, Cavani (Stuani 74) <br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (4-4-2): </strong>Rui Patricio; Ricardo Pereira, Pepe, Fonte, Guerreiro; Bernardo Silva, William Carvalho, Adrien Silva (Quaresma 65&rsquo;), Joao Mario (Fernandes 84&rsquo;); Goncalo Guedes (Andre Silva 74&rsquo;), Ronaldo<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Uruguay 2-1 Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Thong-so-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190048.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190046.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-463-190010.html\">Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: Ronaldo \u0111\u00f3ng phim m\u1ea5t t\u00edch, Seleccao cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"765","checkdouble":"190051"},{"date":"07:44 01/07","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Edinson Cavani b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay.\r\nN.D (TTVN)\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-461-190020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/cavabi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-461-190020.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y Ronaldo im ti\u1ebfng, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Uruguay v\u1ed1n d\u0129 qu\u00e1